The current price currently stands at £10,000 per hit. Half of the payment MUST be required before the hit. After the job has been completed you will transfer the rest of the payment. The payment is BITCOIN ONLY.

I do not accept hits that are placed onto under 18's as I find it unethical and cruel although gender does not matter unlike other services.

When I recieve your email it MUST be ENCRYPTED with PGP or it will simply be ignored. If you do not know how to use PGP just google a simple tutorial. Be sure to leave your public key so I can contact you back.

I will need basic information such as first and last name and also an address. If you do not know this information do not worry, just provide all information possible like email addresses, any used online aliases, facebook accounts etc.

This will however (depending on the information that I need to find) increase the price of the hit to anything between £200 - £1000.

More will be discussed when you get into contact with me.
